¶\n(1) chalazal\n(2) micropylar\n(3) both 1 and 2\n(4) integument\n\nQ15. Amount of DNA in vegetative cell of pollen and synergids isО“ГҮГ¶\n(1) c and 2c\n(2) c and c\n(3) 2c and c\n(4) both 2c\n\nQ16. Number of cytokinesis to form mature embryo sac with 7 cells isО“ГҮГ¶\n(1) six\n(2) seven\n(3) three\n(4) five\n\nQ17. Egg apparatus has number of gametesО“ГҮГ¶\n(1) one\n(2) three\n(3) four\n(4) two\n\nQ18. Egg apparatus is similar to role performed in gymnospermО“ГҮГ¶\n(1) microsporangia\n(2) female gametophyte\n(3) archegonium\n(4) egg cell\n\nQ19. Synchronised pollen release and receptive stigma should be present inО“ГҮГ¶\n(1) Autogamous\n(2) Cleistogamous\n(3) both 1 and 2\n(4) Chasmogamous\n\nQ20. In Viola, which type of pollination surely occursО“ГҮГ¶\n(1) Autogamy\n(2) Xenogamy\n(3) Geitonogamy\n(4) all of the above\n\nQ21. In Viola, which type of pollination can occurО“ГҮГ¶\n(1) Autogamy\n(2) Xenogamy\n(3) Geitonogamy\n(4) all of the above\n\nQ22. Benefit of cleistogamous flower isО“ГҮГ¶\n(1) less variant than chasmogamous\n(2) underground flower\n(3) seed set in absence of pollinator\n(4) all of the above\n\nQ23. In a monoecious flower which is chasmogamous, which is possibleО“ГҮГ¶\n(1) Autogamy\n(2) Geitonogamy\n(3) Xenogamy\n(4) all of the above\n\nQ24. In a monoecious flower which is cleistogamous, which is possibleО“ГҮГ¶\n(1) Autogamy\n(2) Geitonogamy\n(3) Xenogamy\n(4) all of the above\n\nQ25. In a dioecious flower which is chasmogamous, which is possibleО“ГҮГ¶\n(1) Autogamy\n(2) Geitonogamy\n(3) Xenogamy\n(4) both 2 and 3\n\nQ26. In a dioecious plant which is cleistogamous, which is possibleО“ГҮГ¶\n(1) Autogamy\n(2) Geitonogamy\n(3) Xenogamy\n(4) none of the above\n\nQ27. In a dioecious plant which is chasmogamous, which is possibleО“ГҮГ¶\n(1) Autogamy\n(2) Geitonogamy\n(3) Xenogamy\n(4) all of the above\n\nQ28. Chasmogamous flower can be all exceptО“ГҮГ¶\n(1) Autogamous\n(2) Geitonogamous\n(3) Xenogamous\n(4) Cleistogamous\n\nQ29. Xenogamy can occur i